149
00:09:28,250 --> 00:09:29,090
Jun Mo,

150
00:09:30,790 --> 00:09:31,830
are you okay?

151
00:09:32,750 --> 00:09:33,790
I'm okay.

152
00:09:34,410 --> 00:09:35,620
You're okay now.

153
00:09:36,620 --> 00:09:37,580
That's great.

154
00:09:56,200 --> 00:09:57,080
Mr. Mo,

155
00:09:57,080 --> 00:09:59,000
