156
00:09:59,580 --> 00:10:00,830
Look at them carefully.

157
00:10:01,250 --> 00:10:02,450
They all worked here.

158
00:10:29,840 --> 00:10:30,830
Mr. Mo,

159
00:10:31,080 --> 00:10:32,450
I know these people.

160
00:10:32,840 --> 00:10:34,090
They were all honest.

161
00:10:34,500 --> 00:10:36,250
Last night, they conspired

162
00:10:36,250 --> 00:10:37,500
to assassinate Jun Mo.

163
00:10:39,410 --> 00:10:40,450
It's my fault.

164
00:10:40,660 --> 00:10:42,040
I used the wrong people,

165
00:10:42,080 --> 00:10:43,790
letting spies in.

166
00:10:45,630 --> 00:10:47,370
All the people in the villa are unreliable now.

167
00:10:47,660 --> 00:10:48,870
Dismiss them all.

168
00:10:52,580 --> 00:10:53,420
Yes.

169
00:10:53,660 --> 00:10:55,040
I'll handle it right away.

170
00:10:57,540 --> 00:10:58,380
Wait.

