♪Mountains and seas unseen♪

192
00:12:38,570 --> 00:12:39,930
♪Moonlit nights unremembered♪

193
00:12:39,930 --> 00:12:44,410
♪Only regret cannot be measured in years♪

194
00:12:44,730 --> 00:12:46,330
♪We were once so close♪

195
00:12:46,330 --> 00:12:47,770
♪Countless meetings♪

196
00:12:47,770 --> 00:12:52,530
♪Like seeing you anew♪

197
00:12:52,530 --> 00:12:56,370
♪A meeting agreed upon, yet also a parting♪

198
